learning_outcomes.en:
Participants who pass practice
- have contact with real problems of the field;
- have experience of applying the theory to solve practical problems;
- know at least one narrower field in their specialty in more detail;
- can more adequately estimate their knowledge and skills;
- have an experience in working in a collective and developed their social abilities;
- have experiences about everyday working rutine and sense of duty and answer for job.
